Package: lpSolveR
Title: Solve Linear Programming Problems Using Multiple Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Author: 
    Vincent, Ang <123040048@link.cuhk.edu.cn>
    Kevin, Sutario <123040030@link.cuhk.edu.cn>
Maintainer: 
    Vincent, Ang <123040048@link.cuhk.edu.cn>
Description: Provides implementations of linear programming solvers including
    the simplex method and interior point methods. Allows users to solve LP problems
    and compare performance across methods such as runtime, iterations, and solutions.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: ggplot2
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
